"He [Crawford] said, 'I know how much you hate the oil
companies.'  I said, '... I still hate the oil companies but
I'll do you a favor."  Senator Packwood testified that
"...whenever anybody comes in like this and if you're going
to do something anyway, you let them think it's a big
favor."

200.  On July 11, 1990, Senator Packwood recorded in his
