want to retain Ron because, as Ron says, "People hear that
you're tough to get to and they know I can get to you."  I
said, "Well, that's a happy relationship for all of us."
Senator Packwood testified that he is delighted to see Mr.
Crawford's clients because Mr. Crawford does not mislead
him.

201. Mr. Crawford recalls two issues of interest to
